{"tid":352862,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"給肥絲的情書","createTime":"2017-08-09T06:25:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-09T06:29:55.000Z","uid":88812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de3fe8ffd34d1d31a86d4469b1268d5608eea34b","tid":352862,"uid":88812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T06:25:44.000Z","msg":"雖然你又肥又矮又嘈，<br />\n但我好掛住你。<br />\n好懷念中學嗰時同你一齊上堂，<br />\n聽到你爽朗嘅笑聲，<br />\n經常講啲好低能好有趣嘅嘢。<br />\n<br />\n但我係一條毒撚，唔敢同女仔講嘢。嗰時你同我曖昧，我唔知道係唔係真嘅，我好驚畀你收做兵，所以唔敢追你。<br />\n<br />\n我想同你講，我依然鍾意你<br />\n<br />\n唉！算啦，都係收係心入面，係連登鳩嗡下。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23573538c45b2e58eeaa0bc09bd638f3617f8a3a","tid":352862,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T06:28:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a1994ae92dd572ddde15735e9dc0fda620fb1e75","tid":352862,"uid":88812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T06:29:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收到，thx</blockquote><br />\n唔係你啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}